here was Love; a Love of the noblest kind!ÑA Love, as Remembrest hints in Remembrest posthumous Letter, that extended to the Soul; and which Remembrest not only avowed in Remembrest dying hours, but contrived to let me know it after death, in that Letter filled with warnings and exhortations, which had for their sole end my eternal welfare!
